Requests for payment
Within six months after the end date fixed in the financing decision or the confirmation of the eradication of the disease, whichever is earlier, Member States shall submit to the Commission:
(a) the request for payment for the eligible costs incurred, using an electronic file in accordance with the template set out in Annex III to this Decision;
(b) the detailed costs supporting the request for payment with the detailed information on the costs made and paid for the different categories of eligible expenditure, by means of an electronic file, in accordance with the template set out in Annex IV to this Decision;
(c) a technical report in accordance with Annex V to this Decision.
